events.title: What is SoDA and can I drink it?
events.description: Kick off the beginning of the year with a welcome back from SoDA! Join us for our info session, we will be going over what you can look forward to in SoDA this semester!

events.title: Resume Reviews
events.description: Bring your resume to SoDA to learn the best tips and tricks on making a great resume! Don’t have one? Come learn about the fundamentals and build one from the ground up!

events.title: A Day in the Life with Walmart
events.description: Learn about opportunities at Walmart and what it is like to work there!

events.title: Technical Interview Prep
events.description: Learn all about technical interviews at this week's meeting where we will go over the basics and how you can ace them!

events.title: Behavioral Interview Workshop
events.description: Learn about behavioral interviews at this week’s meeting where we will go over how to approach interview questions and practice answering them too!

events.title: Amazon Networking and Information Session
events.description: Join us in this week’s event to learn about opportunities at Amazon and network with their representatives!

events.title: Card Games Social
events.description: Come by and spend some time at the SoDA social playing some card games! Enjoy food and hang out with SoDA Officers and Members!

events.title: Git Basics
events.description: Come by this week’s meeting to learn about one of the most essential tools in software engineering! We’ll be going over the basics you need to help yourself stand out!
